In this question alice and bob have to pic the stones and alice starts first with m = 1

To win the game we have to **minimize the stone picked by the next player** . Both bob and alce follow this creteria to win as both plays optimally.

Now comes the DP part

I have maded a suffix array in which sufix[i] tells me the number of stones from i  to n - 1.

I have maded a function which tells we from where to start (ind) and how many piles i can take (m).

**In this i have itrated till ind + 2m (taking all passible solutions) and took the minimum one means the opponent bob will get the minimum from ind to ind + 2m this will continue for eash othet.**

At last we get the ans.

Also take cate of base conditions

